Interface AnnotationValue.OfAnnotation

All Superinterfaces:
AnnotationValue
Enclosing interface:
AnnotationValue
public static sealed interface AnnotationValue.OfAnnotation extends AnnotationValue
Models an annotation value of an element-value pair. The tag of this value is @.
Since:
24
